headline: The best live chat software on the planet.  We help you buildâ¦
description:
Olark is easy-to-use live chat software that lets you talk to customers on your website. 

Olark can help you track leads, drive sales, increase conversions, and provide great customer service. Real-time visitor information like login name, geographic location, purchase history and cart contents help you personalize every interaction and strengthen customer relationships. 

Sign up and start making your customers happier today!

Click here to sign up for a demo:
https://hello.olark.com/sales

# Someone on your website is ready to chat. Rise to the occasion.
[Request a Demo](http://olark.com/</chatbot-copilot#cp-scroll>)
Simple chat and AI tools that everyone can use. Deliver support, drive sales, and capture more leads to hit your goals.
![An illustration of a blind woman using a computer with a guide dog asleep under her desk.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6481ff76b5ff5f59a69087d3_blind_user_illustration.webp)
![An illustration of a desk with a laptop, plant, and hearing aid sitting on the top.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6481f830724105fa6fcbb495_accessibility_illustration_2x.webp)
## Accessible by design
Adding chat to your website can make it more accessible, but this only works if you choose messaging tools that are created to include people with disabilities.Olark's platform is third-party tested and certified by a third-party to comply with WCAG 2.1 AA standards. This means that the chat widget on your website _and_ the software your team uses to reply to incoming messages will work for disabled people, not against them. 
![A purple and white badge with the words WCAG 2.1AA Certified.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6470d202041bb767ea2e2698_2023_Olark_WCAG-2%202.svg)
[Learn more about accessible chat](http://olark.com/</ada-accessible-live-chat>)
## Multiple ways to communicate in real-time
![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/647a678f28e918e69c9ebdda_greensquiggle.webp)
![A solid purple circle behind the white outline of a waving hand.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6470e10585072710b11d0347_handicon.webp)
### Live Chat
#### Hands-on help from humans
Nothing beats hands-on help from humans. Answer questions in-context on your website with our robust platform, built for teams.
[View Live Chat Features ](http://olark.com/</features>)
![A solid purple circle behind the white outline of a flexing bicep. Below the image, the word PRO is spelled out in white on a pink rectangle.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6488ec387c1ca596f7cc96e7_originalpro.webp)
### Chatbots
#### AI-powered assistant for your agents
There are some tasks only humans can handle. For everything else, we’ll build you a custom bot to tackle the easy stuff.
[Explore AI & Automation Tools](http://olark.com/</chatbot-copilot>)
![A solid purple circle, with a white chat bubble icon and the letters "SMS" in the foreground. Below the circle, the word "BETA" is spelled out in white on a purple rectangle.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6488ec9b646e7274f09c1cf6_originalSMS.webp)
### SMS Texting
#### Mobile-friendly async messaging
For agents and customers on the move, SMS is best. For everything else, we'll build you a custom bot to tackle.
[Join the SMS Waitlist](http://olark.com/</chatbot-copilot#cp-scroll>)
![An illustration meant to depict Artificial Intelligence. ](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6481fec150a2b373bc8de3b3_AI_Illustration.webp)
## Backed by practical AI
You built your business on relationships, and so did we. That’s why we designed chatbox and automation tools to enhance the skills of your people, not replace them.
[Read about human-friendly chatbots](http://olark.com/<https:/www.olark.com/chatbot-copilot>)
## Plays well with others
We know your team is already using systems and software to communicate with customers. While you talk to them, we'll talk to your other tools.Using our flexible API and library of 100+ plugins and integrations, we'll help keep your people and your data on the same page.
[Find your apps in our Integrations Directory](http://olark.com/<https:/www.olark.com/integrations>)
![The Olark logo surrounded by logos of applications Olark integrates with.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6481fed6ec8eb2298374a8ac_integrations_illustration.webp)
## See it to believe it
### Schedule a custom demo with an Olarker.
See the features you like, ask questions, and discuss your needs.
[Book live demoArrow Right](http://olark.com/</chatbot-copilot#cp-scroll>)
### Not ready to talk to sales?
Answer basic questions, design your chatbox, and explore the UI.
[Launch free trialArrow Right](http://olark.com/</signup/create_new_account/trial>)
![Neon illustrations of Olark team members](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6481feeed4c4cfd84d6fe31f_team_illustration.webp)
## Success Stories
Olark dives deep with customers to help them hit their goals. Learn how businesses, nonprofits, and higher ed institutions benefit from including chat as part of their engagement strategy.
![A pink gift box with gold trim. The box is filled with tissue paper and gift items.](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6480a7648e717af6934b4b7b_creative_bag_testimonial.webp)
### Creative Bag
"Don't be overwhelmed by the idea of jumping into chat and the automated bot world. CoPilot was just simple and easy, not intimidating."
![A headshot of Lauren Rotman, Director of E-Commerce, Creative Bag](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6480b17e8b3db6d220f16200_lauren_rotman_creativebag.webp)
Lauren Rotman
Director of E-Commerce, Creative Bag
![A picture of the University of Montana campus quad in Fall. Students walk and skateboard down a path surrounded by Fall foliage. ](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6480d022d1be2ab54eaef802_U_MT_testimonial.webp)
### University of Montana
"Olark has helped us refine our web presence, especially over time. We had metrics of where people were going on our website, but not whether the information was the right information for them."
![A headshot of Joe Hickman, UMT Registrar](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6480d311643c24b582b9789e_Joe_Hickman_UMT.webp)
Joe Hickman
Registrar, University of Montana
![a man, sitting at a desk, viewing two computer monitors displaying Fenetech software](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/6542ba9c7dde913856a535d1_fenetechautomation.webp)
### FeneTech Software
"When you're looking at software for your company, you want to read and digest before you are reached out to... Adjusting our automation settings was a game changer. We see fewer chats now, but more valuable chats."
![The author's headshot](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/646d3c484b3d75dd99420842/646d3c494b3d75dd994208ee_support-dark.svg)
Samantha Hudeck
Manager of Administrative Services

### Olark: The Live Chat Solution for Modern Businesses

**Overview:**
Olark began with a straightforward mission: to be the best live chat software on the planet. Their easy-to-use platform enables businesses to communicate with customers directly on their websites, thereby enhancing customer experience and driving sales. Founded as part of the Y Combinator Batch S09, Olark is located in Ann Arbor, MI, and boasts a team of 28 dedicated employees.

**What They Do:**
Olark provides essential tools for businesses, enabling them to track leads, drive sales, and improve customer service. By leveraging real-time visitor data—think geographic location, purchase history, and cart contents—companies can personalize interactions, ultimately strengthening customer relationships. Some key offerings include:

- **Live Chat**: Real-time support from human agents to tackle customer queries directly on the website.
- **AI Chatbots**: For handling frequently asked questions and automating routine interactions.
- **SMS and Mobile Messaging**: Ensuring support is accessible on-the-go.
- **Accessibility**: Certified to comply with WCAG 2.1 AA standards, Olark ensures that their chat service is accessible to all users.

**Why Choose Olark?**
Their mission revolves around building better customer relationships. With automation and personalization at the core of their services, Olark isn't just about facilitating chats; it's about delivering a better customer experience. Companies like Creative Bag and the University of Montana have successfully integrated Olark into their engagement strategies, reaping the benefits of increased customer satisfaction and refined web presence.

**Call to Action:**
